\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 N-ai auzit niciodat\'e3 despre r\'e3zboaie civile, Compor? \'eentreb\'e3 Trevize.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'cenalt, cu p\'e3rul negru, u\'baor ondulat, el obi\'banuia s\'e3 umble \'fein\'e2ndu-\'bai degetele mari ag\'e3\'feate de centironul de care p\'e3rea s\'e3 nu se despart\'e3 niciodat\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
