\'e3 ac\'feiune.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu sunte\'fei \'een stare de arest, domnule Consilier.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'cen cazul acesta nu trebuie s\'e3 merg cu dumneata, a\'baa e?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ni s-au transmis instruc\'feiuni s\'e3 v\'e3 escort\'e3m la domiciliu.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aatiu \'bai singur drumul.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai s\'e3 v\'e3 protej\'e3m.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 De ce? Sau \'eempotriva cui?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 De orice mul\'feime ce s-ar putea str\'e2nge.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 La miez de noapte?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Tocmai de aceea am a\'bateptat p\'e2n\'e3 la miezul nop\'feii, domnule. Iar acum, pentru binele dumneavoastr\'e3, trebuie s\'e3 v\'e3 invit s\'e3 merge\'fei cu noi. Permite\'fei-mi s\'e3 spun }
{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af nu ca o ameni}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 n\'feare, ci spre informarea dumneavoastr\'e3 }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af c}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'e3
 suntem autoriza\'fei s\'e3 folosim for\'fea la nevoie.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize v\'e3zuse deja crava\'baele neuronice cu care erau \'eenarma\'fei cei doi. Se ridic\'e3 cu un aer care n\'e3d\'e3jdui c\'e3 exprima demnitate:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Acas\'e3, deci... Ori voi descoperi c\'e3 vre\'fei s\'e3 m\'e3 duce\'fei la \'eenchisoare?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu ni s-a ordonat s\'e3 v\'e3 min\'feim, domnule, zise m\'e2ndru locotenentul.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize \'ee\'bai d\'e3du seama c\'e3 se afla \'een prezen\'fea unui profesionist care ar solicita o aprobare chiar \'bai pentru a min\'fei \'bai c\'e3, \'een cazul c\'e2nd i s-ar ordona a\'baa ceva, expresia fe
\'feei \'bai tonul vocii l-ar da imediat de gol.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cer scuze, domnule Locotenent. N-am vrut s\'e3 las a se \'een\'feelege c\'e3 m-a\'ba \'eendoi de cuv\'e2ntul dumitale.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Afar\'e3 erau a\'batepta\'fei de un vehicul de teren. Strada era pustie \'bai nu se vedea \'feipenie de om. Nici vorb\'e3 de mul\'feimi, dar locotenentul se exprimase corect. Nu spusese c\'e3 afar\'e3
 se afla sau se va aduna o mul\'feime. Se referise doar la "orice mul\'feime care s-ar putea str\'e2nge".}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Locotenentul se plasase precaut \'eentre Trevize \'bai vehicul. Trevize nu s-ar fi putut strecura pentru a-\'bai c\'e3uta salvarea prin fug\'e3. Locotenentul urc\'e3 imediat dup\'e3 el \'bai se a\'baez\'e3 \'ee
n spate.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Vehiculul se urni din loc.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Presupun c\'e3 de \'eendat\'e3 ce voi ajunge acas\'e3 voi putea s\'e3-mi v\'e3d, liber \'bai ne\'eengr\'e3dit, de treburile mele \'bai c\'e3, de exemplu, a\'ba putea pleca dac\'e3 am chef.}{
\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Avem ordin s\'e3 nu v\'e3 deranj\'e3m \'een nici un fel, domnule Consilier, dec\'e2t dac\'e3 acest lucru contravine ordinului de a v\'e3 proteja.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Contravine? Ce vrea s\'e3 \'eensemne asta \'een cazul de fa\'fe\'e3?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  \'af Am primit ordin s}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'e3 v\'e3 comunic c\'e3 imediat ce ajunge\'fei acas\'e3 nu pute\'fei pleca. Str\'e3zile nu prezint\'e3 siguran\'fe\'e3, iar eu r\'e3
spund de integritatea dumneavoastr\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Vrei s\'e3 spui c\'e3 voi fi arestat la domiciliu?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu sunt avocat, domnule Consilier. Nu \'batiu ce \'eenseamn\'e3 asta.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Apoi privi drept \'eenainte, \'eens\'e3 \'ee\'bai men\'feinu cotul \'een coasta lui Trevize. Trevize n-ar fi putut s\'e3 fac\'e3 nici o mi\'bacare, oric\'e2t de mic\'e3, f\'e3r\'e3 ca locotenentul s\'e3 nu-\'ba
i dea seama.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Autovehiculul se opri \'een fa\'fea casei micu\'fee din suburbia Flexner. \'cen prezent locuia singur }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Flavella }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'eel p
\'e3r\'e3sise, obosit\'e3 de via\'fea dezordonat\'e3 pe care el era silit s\'e3 o duc\'e3 din pricina numeroaselor angajamente pe care le avea de c\'e2nd devenise Consilier }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af a}{
\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'baa c\'e3 nu erau speran\'fee s\'e3-l a\'batepte cineva.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Acum cobor? \'eentreb\'e3 Trevize.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Voi cobor\'ee eu mai \'eent\'e2i, domnule Con}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 silier. V\'e3 vom eseorta.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Pentru propria-mi siguran\'fe\'e3?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Da, domnule.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'cen cas\'e3 \'eel a\'bateptau dou\'e3 g\'e3rzi. O lamp\'e3 de veghe arunca o lumin\'e3 palid\'e3, iar ferestrele fuseser\'e3 date cu o pelicul\'e3 opac\'e3, astfel c\'e3 din afar\'e3 nimeni nu putea privi \'ee
n cas\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Pentru o cli}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 p\'e3, sim\'fei o revolt\'e3 \'eempotriva acestei \'eenc\'e3lc\'e3ri a intimit\'e3\'feii sale, dup\'e3 care alung\'e3 sentimentul cu o u\'baoar\'e3
 ridicare din umeri. Dac\'e3 nici m\'e3car Consiliul n-a \'eendr\'e3znit s\'e3-l apere \'een \'baedin\'fea Camerei, atunci era sigur c\'e3 propria-i cas\'e3 nu putea deveni peste}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  noapte un castel.}{\f27\fs20 

\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 C\'e2\'fei sunte\'fei cu totul? Un regiment?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu, domnule Consilier, se auzi o voce hot\'e3r\'e2t\'e3 \'bai sigur\'e3. O singur\'e3 persoan\'e3 \'een afara celor pe care le po\'fei vedea \'bai te asigur c\'e3 te a\'batept de mult\'e3
 vreme.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Harla Branno, Primarul Terminusului, ap\'e3ru \'een cadrul u\'baii care d\'e3dea \'een camera de zi.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Avem timp suficient pentru a discuta, de acord?
