\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Precum \'bai-n secolele ce-au urmat, remarc\'e3 Trevize. Ar fi putut servi ca baze pentru pira\'fei \'bai, \'eent\'e2mpl\'e3tor, asta aducea venituri mai substan\'feiale dec\'e2t un comer\'fe
 cinstit.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Asta n-o \'batiu, zise \'eeng\'e2ndurat Pelorat.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20 \'ce}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 n sf\'e2r\'bait, am impresia}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 c\'e3 P\'e3m\'e2ntul ar trebui s\'e3 fie 
primul pe lista planetelor populate, indiferent de ceea ce prefer\'e3 locuitorii s\'e3i. Considerat\'e3 prin defini\'feie drept cea mai veche, nu putea fi ignorat\'e3 \'een secolele de \'eenceput ale civiliza\'feiei Galactice. \'aai odat\'e3 pus\'e3
 pe list\'e3, trebuia s\'e3 r\'e3m\'e2n\'e3 acolo. Aici sigur nu putem invoca iner\'feia social\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Pelorat avu o ezitare \'bai p\'e3ru chinuit de-un g\'e2nd:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 De fapt, exist\'e3 o... o planet\'e3 numit\'e3 P\'e3m\'e2nt pe lista celor populate.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Am \'een\'feeles eu gre\'bait sau ai spus adineaori c\'e3 P\'e3m\'e2ntul nu figureaz\'e3 pe list\'e3? \'eentreb\'e3 Trevize privindu-l \'feint\'e3 pe Pelorat.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu sub numele de p\'e3m\'e2nt. Exist\'e3, totu\'bai, o planet\'e3 numit\'e3 Gaia.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu v\'e3d leg\'e3tura. Gahyah?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Se scrie G-A-I-A. \'censeamn\'e3 "P\'e3m\'e2nt".
\par }{\f446\fs16\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Gaia (sau Gea) \'af zei}{\f443\fs16\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'fe\'e3}{\b\f27\fs16\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs16\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 greac\'e3, personific\'e2nd glia fertil\'e3
, principiul n\'e3sc\'e3tor \'bai subzisten\'feial al vie\'feii,}{\b\f27\fs16\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs16\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 divinitate dual\'e3 care d\'e3ruie\'bate ne\'eencetat via\'fea \'bai \'ee\'bai ia periodic totul \'ee
napoi (n. trad.).}{\f27\fs16 
