\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Prim Orator! vorbi ea rar, f\'e3r\'e3 s\'e3-\'bai mi\'bate buzele sub\'feiri \'bai lipsite de via\'fe\'e3, mai greu de distins acum din cauza palorii chipului. Chiar tu ai afirmat c\'e3
 n-ai dovezi palpabile care s\'e3-\'fei sprijine p\'e3rerea \'bai c\'e3 matematica psihoistoric\'e3 nu}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 indic\'e3 nimic. Ne ceri s\'e3 lu\'e3m o hot\'e3r\'e2re crucial
\'e3 pe baza unui sentiment mistic?}{\f27\fs20 
