\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Acum Novi st\'e3tea \'een fa\'fea lui, timid\'e3, m\'e2ndr\'e3, sfioas\'e3, triumf\'e3toare }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'ee
