\par DUP}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'c3 CE TREVIZE efectu\'e3 un "micro-Salt", Janov Pelorat privi pentru prima oar\'e3-n via\'fea lui cum str\'e3lucitoarea stea deveni un astru ceresc. Apoi, \'een r\'e3stimpul c\'e2
torva zile, Sayshell, cea de-a patra planet\'e3 locuibil\'e3 care era \'bai destina\'feia lor imediat\'e3, crescu \'een m\'e3rime \'bai luminozitate.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Computerul executase o hart\'e3 care acum era proiectat\'e3 pe un ecran portabil pe care Pelorat \'eel \'feinea pe genunchi.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cu siguran\'fea lui, care de-a lungul carierei cobor\'e2se pe c\'e2teva zeci de planete, Trevize spuse:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu te gr\'e3bi, Janov. Trebuie s\'e3 trecem pe la sta\'feia de acces \'eent\'e2i \'bai s-ar putea s\'e3 fie tare plicticos.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Pelorat ridic\'e3 ochii spre el:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Bine\'een\'feeles c\'e3-i doar o formalitate.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Exact. \'aai totu\'bai plicticoas\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Dar tr\'e3im \'een vremuri de pace.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Sigur. Asta }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'eenseamn\'e3 c\'e3 ne vor l\'e3sa s\'e3 trecem. Cu toate astea, se pune problema echilibrului ecologic. Fiecare planet\'e3 are un echilibru \'ba
i nimeni nu vrea s\'e3-l strice. A\'baa c\'e3 e absolut normal s\'e3 se verifice toate navele pentru depistarea unor organisme sau infec\'feii nedorite. O m\'e3sur\'e3 \'een\'feeleapt\'e3 de prevedere.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cred c\'e3 n-avem la bord a\'baa ceva.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu, \'bai se vor convinge. \'cen acela\'bai timp, \'feine seama c\'e3 Sayshell nu e}{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 membr\'e3 a Federa
\'feiei Funda\'feiei, a\'baa c\'e3 sigur o s\'e3 ne re\'fein\'e3 pu\'fein pentru a-\'bai demonstra statutul de independen\'fe\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 O nav\'e3 mic\'e3 se apropie \'bai la bord sosi un func\'feionar vamal de pe Sayshell pentru inspec\'feie. Trevize \'eel salut\'e3 respectuos \'bai precis, amintindu-\'bai de vremea c\'e2nd fusese militar.}{
\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Far Star, }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 de pe Terminus.}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Documentele navei. Ne\'eenarmat
\'e3. Nav\'e3 particular\'e3. Pa\'baaportul meu. Am un pasager. Pofti\'fei pa\'baaportul. Suntem turi\'bati.}{\f27\fs20 
