\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Pelorat se ferea s\'e3 se bage-n s}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 ufletul lui Trevize care}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\sub\langnp1048 ( }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 r\'e3m\'e3
sese nemi\'bacat pe scaun, muncit de g\'e2nduri.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'cen cele din urm\'e3 \'eendr\'e3zni:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Golan, st\'e3m aici toat\'e3 noaptea?
\par Trevize tres\'e3ri:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu, ai dreptate. Ne-am sim\'fei mult mai bine \'eentre oameni. Hai s\'e3 mergem!
\par Pelorat se ridic\'e3 \'bai \'eentreb\'e3 \'een}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 curcat:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 De unde-at\'e2ta lume? Compor spunea c\'e3 e un fel de zi de medita\'feie aici.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af A}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'baa a spus? C\'e2nd am venit \'eencoace circulau vehicule pe drum?
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Da, c}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'e2teva.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Destul de multe, am avut eu impresia. Iar apoi, c\'e2nd am intrat \'een ora\'ba, str\'e3zile erau pustii?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu chiar. Cu toate astea, trebuie s\'e3 recuno\'bati c\'e3 \'een cl\'e3direa asta nu era nimeni.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 A\'baa e. Asta mi-a s\'e3rit \'een ochi. Hai, Janov, mi s-a f\'e3cut foame. Trebuie s\'e3 g\'e3sim un loc unde s\'e3 m\'e2nc\'e3m ceva \'bai cred c\'e3 ne putem permite s\'e3
 alegem ceva ca lumea. \'cen orice caz, s\'e3 g\'e3sim un restaurant unde s\'e3 putem \'eencerca vreo specialitate culinar\'e3 sayshellian\'e3 sau, dac\'e3 ne trece pofta, o s\'e3 ne mul\'feumim cu ni\'bate m\'e2ncare galactic\'e3 standard. Hai, \'bai c
\'e2nd o s\'e3 ne pierdem \'eentre oameni, o s\'e3-\'fei spun ce cred c\'e3 s-a \'eent\'e2mplat de fapt}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  aici.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par 
