\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Bine, hai s\'e3 privim logic lucrurile. S\'e3 presupunem c\'e3 }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 ar fi }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 agent al celei de-a Doua Funda\'fe
