\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ne putem \'eentoarce dup\'e3 ce facem verific\'e3ri \'een Sectorul Sirius.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu \'fei-a trecut prin minte c\'e3 ne-a \'eent\'e2lnit special ca s\'e3 ne determine s\'e3 plec\'e3m din Sayshell? S\'e3 ne ducem oriunde, numai s\'e3 nu r\'e3m\'e2nem aici?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 De ce?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 N-am idee. Ascult\'e3. Se a\'bateptau s\'e3 mergem spre Trantor. }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Tu }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 voiai asta \'ba
