\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Bine\'een\'feeles c\'e3 \'fei se pare, daca ai fost influen\'feat.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ba n-am fost.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Sigur c\'e3 e\'bati gata s\'e3 \'bai juri c\'e3 nu te-a influen\'feat nimeni, mai ales dac\'e3-i adev\'e3rat.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Dac\'e3 m\'e3-ncol\'fee\'bati \'een felul \'e3sta, n-am cum s\'e3 dovedesc contrariul. Ce-ai de g\'e2nd s\'e3 faci?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Voi r\'e3m\'e2ne pe Sayshell. \'aai-o s\'e3 stai \'bai tu cu mine. Nu te pricepi s\'e3 conduci nava f\'e3r\'e3 mine, a\'baa c\'e3 dac\'e3 te-a influen\'feat, Compor are s\'e3 afle cur\'e2nd c
\'e3 a gre\'bait persoana.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Foa}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 rte bine, Golan. Vom r\'e3m\'e2ne aici p\'e2n\'e3 c\'e2nd vom avea motive s\'e3 plec\'e3m. La urma urmei, cel mai grav lucru ce ni s-ar putea \'ee
nt\'e2mpla e s\'e3 nu ne mai \'een\'feelegem \'eentre noi. Hai, prietene, dac\'e3 a\'ba fi fost influen\'feat ai putea s\'e3 m\'e3 determini s\'e3-mi schimb p\'e3rerea \'bai s\'e3 r\'e3m\'e2n al\'e3turi de tine f\'e3r\'e3 s\'e3-\'fei port pic\'e3, a\'ba
