\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Pelorat str\'e2mb\'e3 din nas c\'e2nd se \'eentoarse pe }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Far Star }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'eempreun\'e3 cu Trevize.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize ridic\'e3 nep\'e3s\'e3tor din umeri.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Corpul uman este un mare produc\'e3tor de mirosuri. Instala\'feia de reciclare a aerului nu reu\'bae\'bate s\'e3 le elimine perfect \'bai parfumurile artificiale se suprapun, d\'e2nd na\'ba
tere altor mirosuri nepl\'e3cute.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai presupun c\'e3 mirosul specific al unei nave nu seam\'e3n\'e3 cu al alteia.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Adev\'e3rat, dar ai mai sim\'feit mirosul Planetei Sayshell dup\'e3 ce ai petrecut o or\'e3 pe ea?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu, recunoscu Pelorat.}{\f27\fs20 
