\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Kodell \'ee\'bai aplec\'e3 capul u\'baor \'een fa\'fe\'e3 \'een semn de salut obligatoriu \'eenainte de a \'eencepe discu\'feia cu Primarul. Acest ceremonial era o tradi\'feie ce d\'e3
inuia de pe vremea nefericit\'e3 a Indburilor. Aproape toate se schimbaser\'e3, \'eens\'e3 eticheta r\'e3m\'e3sese aceea\'bai.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Regret \'eent\'e2rzierea, Primare, dar ecourile arest\'e3rii lui Trevize au \'eenceput s\'e3-\'bai croiasc\'e3 loc prin min\'feile anesteziate ale Consilierilor.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Da? f\'e3cu Primarul cu nep\'e3sare. Anticipezi cumva o revolu\'feie de palat?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nici vorb\'e3 de-a\'baa ceva. Control\'e3m situa\'feia. Dar va ie\'bai cu t\'e3r\'e3boi.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Las\'e3-i s\'e3 fac\'e3 t\'e3r\'e3boi. A\'baa se vor sim\'fei mai bine, iar eu... eu o s\'e3 stau deoparte. Presupun c\'e3 opinia public\'e3 va fi, \'een general, de partea mea.}{\f27\fs20 

\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cred c\'e3 da. Mai ales pe Terminus. Nu cred c\'e3 celor din afara Terminusului le pas\'e3 ce i se \'eent\'e2mpl\'e3 unui Consilier care a luat-o pu\'fein razna.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Mie-mi pas\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Aha. Ve\'bati noi?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Liono, spuse Primarul. Spune-mi tot ce \'batii despre Sayshell.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu-s carte ambulant\'e3 de istorie, \'eei r\'e3spunse Liono Kodell z\'e2mbind.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu vreau istorie. Adev\'e3rul. De ce este Sayshell independent? Uite-aici. (Ar\'e3t\'e3 spre por\'feiunea ro\'baie de pe harta holografic\'e3 \'bai undeva, \'ee
n interiorul spiralelor, se vedea o zon\'e3 alb\'e3. \'cenconjurat\'e3 din toate p\'e3r\'feile, aproape \'eenghi\'feit\'e3, \'bai cu toate astea, reprezentat\'e3 prin alb.) Harta nici n-arat\'e3 m\'e3car ro\'baul care semnific\'e3 un aliat loial.}{
\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Kodell ridic\'e3 neputincio}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 s din umeri:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Oficial nu ne e aliat \'bai problema loialit\'e3\'feii nu se pune, \'eens\'e3 nu ne-a creat niciodat\'e3 probleme. Are o pozi\'feie de neutralitate.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20 \'ce}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 n regul\'e3. Atunci prive\'bate aici. (\'aai Branno atinge un buton. Culoarea ro\'baie cuprinse \'bai alte regiuni, acoperind practic jum\'e3
tate din Galaxie.) Acesta era teritoriul cucerit de Cat\'e2r la vremea mor\'feii}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 lui. Dac\'e3 te ui\'fei mai atent, vei vedea Uniunea Sayshell. Complet \'eenconjurat
\'e3. E singura enclav\'e3 pe care Cat\'e2rul a l\'e3sat-o liber\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Era neutr\'e3 \'bai pe vremea aceea.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cat\'e2rul}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 nu prea respecta neutralitatea.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Se pare c\'e3 a f\'e3cut-o \'een cazul de fa\'fe\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Se pare. }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Dar ce reprezint\'e3 Sayshell?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nimic! spuse Kodell. Crede-m\'e3, Primare, va fi a noastr\'e3 c\'e2nd vom dori.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Sigur? \'aai totu\'bai nu-i a noastr\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nici nu sim\'feim nevoia ei.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Bra}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 nno se a\'baez\'e3 greoi pe un scaun \'bai, trec\'e2ndu-\'bai m\'e2na peste butoane, stinse reprezentarea Galaxiei.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cred c\'e3 acum vrem s\'e3 fie a noastr\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 N-am \'een\'feeles.}{\f27\fs20 
