\par }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 A\'bateptar\'e3. Se obi\'banuir\'e3 cur\'e2nd cu asta. R\'e3maser\'e3 \'een preajma Gaiei mai mult timp dec\'e2t le trebuise pentru a str\'e3bate distan\'fea de la Terminus p\'e2n\'e3 la Sayshell.}{\f27\fs20 

\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize program\'e3 computerul pentru declan\'baarea automat\'e3 a alarmei \'bai-\'bai permise s\'e3 mo\'fe\'e3ie cu nep\'e3sare pe}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  un scaun capitonat.}{\f27\fs20 

\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Tocmai de aceea se trezi speriat c\'e2nd alarma \'eencepu s\'e3 sune. Pelorat intr\'e3 \'een camera lui Trevize, ar\'e3t\'e2nd Ia fel de zdruncinat Alarma \'eel prinsese \'een timp ce se b\'e3rbierea. }{
\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ai primit vreun mesaj? \'eentreb\'e3 el.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu, \'eei r\'e3spunse Trevize }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 agitat. Ne }{\i\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 deplas\'e3m.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ne deplas\'e3m? \'cencotro?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 C\'e3tre sta\'feia spa\'feial\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cum a\'baa?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu \'batiu. Motoarele au pornit, iar computerul nu vrea s\'e3-mi r\'e3spund\'e3 la comenzi... dar ne deplas\'e3m. Janov, am fost captura\'fei. Ne-am apropiat prea mult de Gaia.}{\f27\fs20 

