\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Pe chipul de obicei lipsit de expresie al lui Pelorat ap\'e3ru o expresie de stupefac\'feie. \'centreb\'e3 nesigur:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 E\'bati uman\'e3?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Femeia deschise ochii mari, arcuindu-\'bai spr\'e2ncenele \'bai str\'e2mb\'e3 din buze. Din gestul acesta nu se putea deduce dac\'e3 auzea o limb\'e3 necunoscut\'e3 \'bai ne\'een\'feeleas\'e3, sau dac\'e3 \'een
\'feelegea limbajul, dar \'eentrebarea o punea pe g\'e2nduri.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ea duse m\'e2na spre partea st\'e2ng\'e3 a costumului, care se desf\'e3cu de parc\'e3 ar fi avut balamale. P\'e3\'bai afar\'e3 din costum \'bai acesta r\'e3mase o clip\'e3 \'een pozi\'feie vertical\'e3
 apoi, cu un sunet ce aducea cu un oftat, se pr\'e3bu\'bai la podea.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Acum, dup\'e3 ce ie\'baise din costumul spa\'feial, femeia p\'e3rea \'bai mai t\'e2n\'e3r\'e3. \'cembr\'e3c\'e3mintea \'eei era larg\'e3 \'bai translucid\'e3, iar pu\'feinele articol}{
\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 e intime}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 se vedeau ca ni\'bate umbre. Roba de deasupra \'eei venea p\'e2n\'e3 la genunchi.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Avea s\'e2nii mici \'bai talia sub\'feire, cu \'baolduri pline \'bai rotunde. Picioarele bine f\'e3cute aveau gleznele fine \'bai gra\'feioase. P\'e3rul}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{
\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 negru \'bai bogat \'eei c\'e3dea pe umeri, buzele pline p\'e3reau u\'baor asimetrice, iar ochii mari \'bai c\'e3prui privir\'e3 \'een jur, apoi spre picioare \'bai rezolv\'e3 dilema, ar\'e3t\'e2nd c\'e3
 pricepea limbajul lor:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu }{\i\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 ar\'e3t }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 uman\'e3?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Vorbea Galactica Standard cu o ezitare abia detectabil\'e3, p\'e3r\'e2nd c\'e3 face un mic efort pentru a pronun\'fea foa}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 rte corect.
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Pelorat \'eencuviin\'fe\'e3 cu o mi\'bacare a capului, \'eenso\'feit\'e3 de un z\'e2mbet:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 N-a\'ba putea nega asta. Foarte uman\'e3. \'cenc\'e2nt\'e3tor de uman\'e3.
\par T\'e2n\'e3ra \'ee\'bai desf\'e3cu bra\'feele larg de parc\'e3 i-ar fi invitat s\'e3 o priveasc\'e3 mai de aproape.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 A\'baa sper \'bai eu, domnilor. Mul\'fei b\'e3rba\'fei ar muri dup\'e3 corpul acesta.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 A\'ba prefera s\'e3 tr\'e3iesc pentru el, gl\'e3sui Pelorat, cu un aer galant care-l lu\'e3 \'bai pe el prin surprindere.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Bun\'e3 alegere, spuse femeia cu solemnitate. Corpul acesta na\'bate \'baoapte \'bai extaz.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 R\'e2se, iar Pelorat porni \'bai el s\'e3 r\'e2d\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize, care r\'e3m\'e3sese \'eencruntat \'bai t\'e3cut \'een timpul acestui schimb de vorbe galante, g\'e3si momentul s\'e3 \'eentrebe:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ce v\'e2rst\'e3 ai?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Femeia \'eencet\'e3 s\'e3 r\'e2d\'e3 \'bai r\'e3spunse cu seriozitate: }{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Dou\'e3zeci \'bai trei, domnilor.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 De ce-ai venit? Cu ce scop ne vizitezi?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Am venit s\'e3 v\'e3-so\'feesc pe Gaia, r\'e3spunse ea, rotunjind u\'baor vocalele \'een diftongi, semn c\'e3 nu st\'e3p\'e2nea la perfec\'feie Galactica Standard.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 S\'e3 ne-nso\'feeasc\'e3 }{\i\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 o fat\'e3?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ea deveni dintr-o dat\'e3 mai b\'e3\'feoas\'e3, vr\'e2nd s\'e3 le dovedeasc\'e3}{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 lui Trevize \'bai lui Pelorat c\'e3 era st
\'e3p\'e2n\'e3 pe situa\'feie:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Eu reprezint Gaia la fel de bine ca oricare altul. Dac\'e3 s-a \'eent\'e2mplat s\'e3 fiu eu de tur\'e3 pe sta\'feie...}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Tura }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 ta? }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Erai singur\'e3 la bordul sta\'feiei?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Nici nu trebuie mai multe persoane, r}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'e3spunse ea semea\'fe\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai acum nu-i nimeni pe ea}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 ?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Sta\'feia nu e p\'e3r\'e3sit\'e3 dac\'e3 eu lipsesc de acolo. }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ea }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 r\'e3m\'e2ne.
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Ea? La ce te referi?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 La sta\'feie. Ea este Gaia. N-are nevoie de mine c\'e2t\'e3 vreme v\'e3 re\'feine nava.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Atunci tu ce faci pe sta\'feie?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Datoria.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Pelorat \'eel apucase de m\'e2nec\'e3 pe Trevize \'bai-l tr\'e3sese u\'baor. Repet\'e3 gestul \'bai-i spuse \'een \'baoapt\'e3:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Golan, nu mai }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'feipa la ea. Nu vezi ce t\'e2n\'e3r\'e3 e? Las\'e3-m\'e3 pe mine s\'e3 vorbesc cu ea.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize se smuci furios, dar Pelorat i-o lu\'e3 \'eenainte \'bai \'eentreb\'e3:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Domni\'baoar\'e3, cum te nume\'bati?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Chipul ei se lumin\'e3 \'eentr-un z\'e2mbet larg, ca reac\'feie la tonul mai bl\'e2nd, \'bai r\'e3spunse:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Bliss.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Bliss? repet}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'e3 Pelorat. Ce nume frumos. Dar nu e singurul, nu-i-a\'baa?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Fire}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'bate. Era caraghios c\'e3 am un nume format dintr-o silab\'e3. S-ar putea repeta pe fiecare sec\'feiune \'bai nu ne-am mai putea deosebi, iar b\'e3rba\'fe
ii ar muri lu\'e2nd un trup drept altul. Numele meu complot e Blissenobiarella.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'dei se umple gura pronun\'fe\'e2ndu-l.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Poftim? Cu numai }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'baapte silabe? Nu-i lung deloc. Am prieteni cu nume din cincisprezece silabe \'bai nu mai prididesc \'eencerc\'e2nd tot felul de combina\'fe
