 are un miros... greu de suportat, interveni Bliss.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Atunci de ce n-ai spus nimic? m\'e2r\'e2i Trevize.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Din polite\'fee. Doar eram oaspete.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai-acum ai uitat de polite\'fee?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Acum sunt pe lumea mea. }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Tu }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 e\'bati oaspete, a\'baa c\'e3 te rog s\'e3 fii politicos.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Are probabil dreptate, Golan. Avem cum s\'e3 aerisim nava? se b\'e3g\'e3 \'een vorb\'e3 Pe}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 lorat.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Da, i-o retez\'e3 Trevize, sigur, dac\'e3 aceast\'e3 mic\'e3 domni\'baoar\'e3 ne asigur\'e3 c\'e3 nu se va atinge nimeni de nav\'e3. Ne-a dovedit deja c\'e3 are puteri neobi\'banuite asupra ei.
}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Bliss \'ee\'bai arcui trupul \'bai nu se l\'e3s\'e3 mai prejos:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu sunt chiar mic\'e3 \'bai dac\'e3-\'fei \'eenchipui c\'e3 se aerise\'bate dac\'e3 o las \'een pace, atunci a\'baa o sa fac.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Bine, }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'bai-acum ne duci la omul c\'e3ruia \'eei spune\'fei Gaia?
\par Bliss p\'e3rea amuzat\'e3:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trev, nu \'batiu dac\'e3 o s\'e3 m\'e3 crezi. }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Eu sunt }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Gaia.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize \'eenm\'e3rmuri. Auzise de nenum\'e3rate ori fraza: "a-\'bai aduna min\'feile" folosit\'e3 metaforic, \'eens\'e3 abia acum sim\'fei pe propria-i piele adev\'e3rul pe care-l exprima ea. Reu\'bai s\'e3 
