\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Tu?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Da. \'aai p\'e3m\'e2ntul. \'aai pomii aceia. \'aai iepurele acela, ascuns \'eentre ierburi. \'aai b\'e3rbatul pe care-l vezi umbl\'e2nd prin livad\'e3. \'centreaga planet\'e3 \'bai tot ce vie
\'feuie\'bate pe ea \'eenseamn\'e3 Gaia. Suntem indivizi }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af organisme separate \'af dar cu to}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'feii \'eemp\'e3rt\'e3\'baim o con\'batiin\'fe\'e3 comun\'e3
. Planeta are o parte infim\'e3 din aceast\'e3 con\'batiin\'fe\'e3, diferitele forme de via\'fe\'e3 \'ee\'bai au \'bai ele partea lor mai mare sau mai mic\'e3, iar fiin\'feele umane, cea mai mare parte.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize, cred c\'e3 vrea s\'e3 spun\'e3 c\'e3 Gaia e un fel de con\'batiin\'fe\'e3 de grup, explic\'e3 Pelorat.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize aprob\'e3 d\'e2nd din cap:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Asta am \'een\'feeles \'bai eu. Bliss, \'een cazul acesta, cine conduce lumea?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Se conduce singur\'e3. Copacii aceia cresc \'een \'bairuri drepte \'bai ordonate din propria lor voin\'fe\'e3. Se \'eenmul\'feesc doar \'een m\'e3sura \'een care e nevoie pentru a-i \'ee
nlocui pe cei care mor. Fiin\'feele umane recolteaz\'e3 merele de care au nevoie; celelalte animale, inclusiv insectele, consum\'e3 partea ce}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  li se cuvine, dar nimic mai mult.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai zici c\'e3 insectele \'batiu ce li se cuvine? \'eentreb\'e3 ironic Trevize.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20 \'ce}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 ntr-un fel, da. Plou\'e3 c\'e2nd trebuie \'bai uneori plou\'e3 toren\'feial c\'e2nd este necesar, \'bai uneori se-nt\'e2mpl\'e3 \'bai c\'e2te-o perioad\'e3 de secet\'e3 pentru c
\'e3 \'bai }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 asta }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 e}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 ste necesar\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai ploaia \'batie \'bai ea c\'e2nd s\'e3 cad\'e3?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Da, r\'e3spunse Bliss cu seriozitate. Nu se-nt\'e2mpl\'e3 la fel \'bai-n organismul t\'e3u? Celulele \'batiu ce s\'e3 fac\'e3. \'aatiu c\'e2nd s\'e3 produc\'e3 anumite substan\'fee \'bai c\'e2
nd s\'e3 inhibe acest proces, iar c\'e2nd produc respectiva substan\'fe\'e3, ele \'batiu ce cantit\'e3\'fei sunt necesare, \'bai nu secret\'e3 nici mai mult, nici mai pu\'fein. Fiecare dintre celule este, \'eentr-o anumit\'e3 m\'e3sur\'e3, o uzin\'e3
 chimic\'e3 independent\'e3, dar toate \'ee\'bai extrag materia prim\'e3 dintr-o surs\'e3 comun\'e3, adus\'e3 de un sistem de transport ce le apar\'feine deopotriv\'e3 \'bai toate \'ee\'bai elimin\'e3 reziduurile \'ee
ntr-o serie de canale comune. Toate acestea contribuie la formarea unei con\'batiin\'fee de grup.
\par Entuziasmat, Pelorat exclam\'e3:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Extraordinar. Vrei s\'e3 spui c\'e3 planeta e un superorganism \'bai c\'e3 tu e\'bati o celul\'e3 a lui.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Am \'eencercat o analogie, n-am spus c\'e3 totul merge p\'e2n\'e3 la identificare. Suntem analogii celulelor, dar nu ne identific\'e3m cu ele, \'een\'feelegi?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 P\'e3i, \'een ce fel nu sunte\'fei celule? \'eencerc\'e3 Trevize s-o \'eencurce.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai noi \'een\'baine suntem construi\'fei din celule \'bai avem o con\'batiin\'fe\'e3 de grup, dac\'e3 vorbim din punctul acesta de vedere. Aceast\'e3 con\'batiin\'fe\'e3
 a organismului individual, a unei fiin\'fee, umane, \'een cazul meu...}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cu un organism dup\'e3 care mor b\'e3rba\'feii...}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Exact. Con\'batiin\'fea mea e mult mai avansat\'e3 dec\'e2t cea a unei celule individuale. Faptul c\'e3 noi, la r\'e2ndul nostru, suntem o p\'e3rticic\'e3 dintr-o con\'batiin\'fe\'e3
 de grup mai cuprinz\'e3toare, situat\'e3 la un nivel superior, nu ne reduce la nivelul celulelor. Eu r\'e3m\'e2n o fiin\'fe\'e3 uman\'e3 }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af dar deasupra noastr}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'e3
 se afl\'e3 o con\'batiin\'fe\'e3 de grup pe care n-o pot cuprinde, a\'baa cum o celul\'e3 din structura mu\'bachiului biceps nu poate cuprinde con\'batiin\'fea mea de sine.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cineva a ordonat sechestrarea navei noastre. Cine? \'eentreb\'e3 Trevize.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20 \'ce}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 n nici un caz cineva anume. Gaia a ordonat. N}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 oi to\'fei am vrut asta.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai copacii \'bai p\'e3m\'e2ntul, Bliss?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Au avut o contribu\'feie foarte mic\'e3, dar sigur\'e3. Ascult\'e3, dac\'e3 un muzician ar scrie o simfonie, \'eentrebi care celul\'e3 din corpul lui a ordonat compozi\'feia \'bai care celul
\'e3 a supravegheat arhitectura ei?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai, dup\'e3 c\'e2te \'een\'feeleg, g\'e2ndirea comun\'e3, ca s\'e3 zicem a\'baa, a con\'batiin\'feei de grup este mult mai puternic\'e3 dec\'e2t g\'e2ndirea unui individ, spuse Pelorat, a
\'baa cum un mu\'bachi e mai puternic dec\'e2t o celul\'e3 individual\'e3 din acel mu\'bachi. Prin urmare, Gaia a capturat nava noastr\'e3 de la distan\'fe\'e3, control\'e2nd computerul, chiar dac\'e3 individual, nici o minte de pe planet\'e3
 n-ar fi putut s-o fac\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ai \'een\'feeles perfect, Pel, \'eel \'eencuraja Bliss.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Tot a\'baa am priceput \'bai eu, zise Trevize. Nu-i chiar a\'baa de complicat. Dar ce vre\'fei de la noi? N-am venit cu inten\'feii du\'bam\'e3noase. Voiam s\'e3 afl\'e3
m anumite lucruri. De ce ne-a\'fei capturat?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ca s\'e3 discut\'e3m cu voi?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Puteam s\'e3 r\'e3m\'e2nem pe nava noastr\'e3 dac\'e3 dorea\'fei numai at\'e2t.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu cu mine ve\'fei vorbi, spuse Bliss cu gravitate.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Dar nu faci parte d}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 in con\'batiin\'fea de grup?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Da, dar nu pot zbura ca pas\'e3rea, b\'e2z\'e2i ca o insect\'e3 sau cre\'bate \'eenait\'e3 ca un copac. Fac ceea ce m\'e3 pricep \'bai nu trebuie s\'e3 v\'e3 informez eu, de\'bai mi s-ar putea 
\'eencredin\'fea informa\'feiile care v\'e3 intereseaz\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cine-a hot\'e3r\'e2t asta?
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Noi }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 to\'fei.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai cine ne va spune ceea ce dorim s\'e3 \'batim?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Dom.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cine-i Dom?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Numele lui complet este Endomandiovizamarondayaso \'bai a\'baa mai departe, spuse Bliss. Fiecare i se adreseaz\'e3 folosind silaba pe care-o consider\'e3 potrivit\'e3, dar \'eel \'ba
tiu ca Dom, \'bai cred c-ar fi bine s\'e3-i spune\'fei la fel. Probabil c\'e3 apar\'feine Gaiei mai mult dec\'e2t oricare altul dintre noi \'bai locuie\'bate pe insula asta. El a cerut s\'e3 v\'e3 vad\'e3 \'bai i s-a aprobat.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cine a aprobat? \'eentreb\'e3 Trevize, dar g\'e3si r\'e3spunsul aproape imediat: A. da, \'batiu cum; voi to\'fei.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Bliss \'eel aprob\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai c\'e2nd \'eel vom \'eent\'e2lni pe Dom? se interes\'e3 Pelorat.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Imediat. Dac\'e3 m\'e3 urma\'fei, o s\'e3 v\'e3 duc la el chiar acum, Pel. \'aai tu e\'bati a\'bateptat, Trev.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai dup\'e3 aceea vei pleca? \'eentreb\'e3 Pelorat.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Vrei s\'e3 r\'e3m\'e2n, Pel?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ca s\'e3 fiu sincer,}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  da.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 A\'baa se \'eent\'e2mpl\'e3 mereu, spuse Bliss, p\'e3\'baind \'eenaintea lor pe un drum bine pietruit care ocolea livada. C\'e2t ai zice pe\'bate le \'bai cad cu tronc b\'e3rba\'feilor. Chiar 
\'bai cei v\'e2rstnici se las\'e3 cuprin\'bai de ardoare tinereasc\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Pelorat izbucni \'een r\'e2s:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ardoarea t}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 inereasc\'e3 s-a cam stins, Bliss, dar cred c\'e3 s-ar aprinde din nou, \'bai n-ar fi numai din pricina ta.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu te nelini\'bati, ea \'eenc\'e3 exist\'e3. Pot s\'e3 fac minuni, \'eei spuse Bliss.
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Trevize }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'eentreb\'e3 ner\'e3bd\'e3tor:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Dup\'e3 ce ajungem unde trebuie, c\'e2t vom avea de a\'bateptat p\'e2n\'e3 vine acest Dom?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 El }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 v\'e3 a\'bateapt\'e3 }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 pe voi. }{
\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 De altfel, }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Dom-prin-Gaia }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 a trudit ani de zile ca s\'e3 v\'e3 aduc\'e3 aici.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize r\'e3mase cu un picior \'een aer, uit\'e2nd s\'e3 mai p\'e3\'baeasc\'e3, \'bai privi pe furi\'ba spre Pelorat care-i spuse pe mute\'bate: Ai avut dreptate.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 F\'e3r\'e3 a pr}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 ivi spre ei, Bliss rosti calm:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trev, \'batiu c\'e3 ai b\'e3nuit c\'e3 Eu/noi/Gaia ne interes\'e3m de voi,}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Eu/noi/Gaia? \'eeng\'e2n\'e3 Pelorat cu jum\'e3tate de gur\'e3.
\par Ea se \'eentoarse spre el \'bai-i z\'e2mbi:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Avem al\'e3turi de diferite pronume pentru a exprima nuan\'feele de individualitate existente pe Gaia. Vi le-a\'ba putea explica dar, p\'e2n\'e3 una-alta, de\'bai "Eu/noi/Gaia" pare cam st\'e2
ngaci, sugereaz\'e3 destul de exact ce vreau s\'e3 comunic. Hai, ce-ai r\'e3mas a\'baa, Trev? Dom ne a\'bateapt\'e3 \'bai n-a\'ba vrea s\'e3 te fac s\'e3 mergi \'eempotriva voin\'feei tale. \'ce\'fei d\'e3 un sentiment nepl\'e3cut dac\'e3 nu e\'bati ob
\'banuit cu a\'baa ceva.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize porni. Privirea pe care i-o arunc\'e3 lui Bliss tr\'e3da o ad\'e2nc\'e3 ne\'eencredere.}{\f27\fs20 
