\'e2n\'e3 c\'e2nd ea degenereaz\'e3 \'een poveste.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Dom, noi, istoricii, cunoa\'batem \'eendeaproape fenomenul. Exist\'e3 o anumit\'e3 preferin\'fe\'e3 pentru pove\'bati. \'cen urm\'e3 cu cir
ca cincisprezece secole, Liebel Gennerat a afirmat: "Falsul dramatism compenseaz\'e3 abunden\'fea de elemente plicticoase." Acum afirma\'feia asta se nume\'bate Legea lui Gennerat.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Adev}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'e3rat? f\'e3cu Dom. \'aai eu care credeam c\'e3-i un comentariu cinic din partea mea. Ei bine. Legea lui Gennerat confer\'e3 farmec \'ba
i imprecizie istoriei noastre trecute. \'aatii ce-i acela un robot?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Am aflat pe Sayshell, r\'e3spunse sec Trevize.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 A\'fei v\'e3zut vreunul?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu, am fost \'eentreba\'fei \'bai dac-am spus c\'e3 n-am v\'e3zut, ni s-a explicat}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20 \'ce}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 n\'feeleg. Umanitatea a tr\'e3it demult cu robo\'fei, dar asta n-a dat}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 rezultate bune.}{
