i Golan Trevize proiect\'e3 imaginea fiec\'e3reia pe c\'e2te o}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 jum\'e3tate de ecran.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ambele apar\'feineau Funda\'feiei. Una era exact ca }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Far Star }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'bai apar\'feinea ne\'eendoielnic lui Compor. Cealalt\'e3 p
\'e3rea mai mare \'bai mult mai puternic\'e3.
\par Se \'eentoarse c\'e3tre Bliss \'bai-o \'eentreb\'e3:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 A\'baa, \'batii ce se-nt\'e2mpl\'e3 acum? Po\'fei s\'e3-mi dai vreo sugestie?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Da! Dar nu te alarma. Nu-\'fei vor face nici un r\'e3u.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 De ce-i toat\'e3 lumea convins\'e3 c\'e3 tremur de fric\'e3? \'eentreb\'e3 Trevize cert\'e3re\'fe.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Las-o s\'e3 vorbeasc\'e3,}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Golan. Nu te r\'e3sti la ea, \'eel \'eendemn\'e3 gr\'e3bit Pelorat.}{
\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize ridic\'e3 bra\'feele \'eemp\'e3ciuitor:
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Nu m}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'e3 r\'e3stesc. Vorbe\'bate, doamn\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Pe nava mare se afl\'e3 c\'e2rmuitorul Funda\'feiei voastre. Cu ea...}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize nu-\'bai putu re\'feine uimirea:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 C\'e2rmuitorul? Te referi la B\'e3tr\'e2na Doamn\'e3 Branno?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu acesta-i e}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  titlul, r\'e3spunse Bliss, u\'baor amuzat\'e3. Dar la ea m-am referit. (F\'e3cu o pauz\'e3 ca \'bai cum ar fi ascultat cu aten\'fe
ie glasul organismului din care f\'e3cea, parte.) O cheam\'e3 Harlabranno}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 . }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Mi se pare ciudat c\'e3 are doar patru silabe c\'e2nd ocup\'e3 o asemenea func\'feie pe l
umea ei, dar presupun c\'e3 a\'baa}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 se obi\'banuie\'bate acolo.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 A\'baa cred \'bai eu, r\'e3spunse posomor\'e2t Trevize. B\'e3nuiesc c\'e3 o s\'e3-i spui Brann. Dar ce caut\'e3 aici? De ce nu se afl\'e3 pe... a, \'een\'feeleg. Gaia a atras-o \'ba
i pe ea. De ce?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Bliss ignor\'e3 \'eentrebarea \'bai spuse:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Al\'e3turi de ea se afl\'e3 Lionokodell, cinci silabe, de\'bai \'eei e}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 subordonat. Mi se pare o lips\'e3
 de respect, cu toate c\'e3 ocup\'e3 o func\'feie oficial\'e3 suspus\'e3 \'een lumea ta. Mai sunt al\'fei patru care se ocup\'e3 de armele navei. Vrei s\'e3 \'batii cum \'eei cheam\'e3?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu. \'cen\'feeleg c\'e3 pe cealalt\'e3 nav\'e3 e un b\'e3rbat, Munn Li Compor, care reprezint\'e3 a Doua Funda\'feie. A\'fei pus fa\'fe\'e3-n fa\'fe\'e3 cele dou\'e3 Funda\'feii.}{
\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 De ce?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu tocmai, Trev,}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 vreau s\'e3 zic Trevize...}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Hai, las\'e3, spune-mi cum vrei. Nu-mi mai pas\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Bine, Trev. Compor a p\'e3r\'e3sit nava \'bai a fost \'eenlocuit de dou\'e3 persoane. Una este Storgendibal, o for\'fe\'e3 a celei de-a Doua Funda\'feii, supranumit Orator.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 O persoan\'e3 cu func\'feie important\'e3? \'cemi imaginez c\'e3 are}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 puteri mentale, a\'baa-i?}{
\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Desigur. Considerabile.
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Po}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'fei s\'e3-i rezi\'bati?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Fire\'bate. A doua persoan\'e3 de pe nava lui este Gaia.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Unul dintre oamenii }{\i\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 vo\'batri?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Da. Se nume\'bate Suranoviremblastiran. Ar trebui s\'e3 aib\'e3 un nume mai}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
lung, dar a stat mult timp departe de mine/noi/restul.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai poate s\'e3 \'fein\'e3 sub control un personaj at\'e2t de puternic de pe a Doua Funda\'feie?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu ea, ci Gaia \'eel \'feine \'een str\'e2nsoare. Ea/eu/noi/to\'fei putem s\'e3-l strivim.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai vrea Gaia s\'e3 fac\'e3 a\'baa ceva? S\'e3-i \'eenfr\'e2ng\'e3 pe el \'bai pe Branno? Ce-nseamn\'e3 asta? Gaia vrea s\'e3 distrug\'e3 Funda\'feiile \'bai s\'e3 \'ee
ntemeieze propriul ei Imperiu Galactic? Iar\'e3\'bai }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cat\'e2rul? Unul}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'bai mai puternic?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu, nu Trev. Nu te fr\'e3m\'e2nta. Nu trebuie. To\'fei trei sunt \'een impas \'bai a\'bateapt\'e3.
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Ce?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Hot\'e3r\'e2rea ta.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Iar o luam de la \'eenceput. }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ce }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 hot\'e3r\'e2re? De ce tocmai }{
\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 eu?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Te rog, Trev, zisg Bliss. \'dei se va explica \'een cur\'e2nd. Eu/noi/ea}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  am spus tot ce am putut.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
