\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Vreau s\'e3 r\'e3m\'e2n aici. Nici nu-mi vine s\'e3 cred. P\'e2n\'e3 acum c\'e2teva s\'e3pt\'e3m\'e2ni duceam o via\'fe\'e3 solitar\'e3 pe Terminus, a\'baa cum am tr\'e3
it zeci de ani, absorbit de documente, \'bai de propriile mele g\'e2nduri, fericit \'een felul meu, dar veget\'e2nd. Apoi peste noapte am devenit c\'e3l\'e3tor prin spa\'feiu, m-am trezit \'een}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{
\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 mijlocul unei crize de propor\'feii galactice \'bai... s\'e3 nu r\'e2zi, Golan, am g\'e3sit-o pe Bli}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 ss.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu r\'e2d, Janov, \'eel asigur\'e3 Trevize, dar crezi c\'e3 e bine ce faci?}{\f27\fs20 
