t de mult. S-a explicat mul\'feumitor de bine c\'e3 a fost prima lume cu un sistem ecologic dezvoltat \'bai echilibrat \'bai cu o via\'fe\'e3}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 inteligent\'e3
. Eternii, \'ee\'bai aminte\'bati?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Da, sigur. \'aai ai}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 de g\'e2nd s\'e3 stai pe Gaia?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Bine\'een\'feeles. P\'e3m\'e2ntul apar\'feine trecutului, iar eu sunt s\'e3tul de istorie. Gaia reprezint\'e3 viitorul.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu e\'bati o parte a Gaiei, Janov. Crezi c\'e3 vei putea deveni o parte a ei?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Bliss spune c\'e3 din punct de vedere intelectual, dac\'e3 nu biologic, a\'ba putea. Are s\'e3 m\'e3 ajute, \'een\'feelegi?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Dar dac\'e3 ea }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 este }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 parte component\'e3 a Gaiei, cum ve\'fei putea s\'e3 tr\'e3i\'fei al\'e3turi, s\'e3}
{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 ave\'fei un punct de vedere comun \'bai interese...}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Se aflau undeva \'een aer }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 liber \'bai Trevize contempl\'e3 grav insula rodnic\'e3 \'bai lini\'batit\'e3, marea \'bai, la orizont, o alt\'e3 insul\'e3 ce p\'e3rea \'ee
mpurpurat\'e3}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 din cauza distan\'feei... toate radiind calm, via\'fe\'e3, civiliza\'feie \'bai unitate.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Janov, rosti el, ea e o lume; tu doar un minuscul individ. Dac}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'e3 se va plictisi de tine? E t\'e2n\'e3r\'e3...}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 M-am g\'e2ndit, Golan. Numai la asta mi-a fost g\'e2ndul \'een ultimele zile. Nu sunt chiar un prost\'e3nac romantic. S-ar putea s\'e3 se plictiseasc\'e3 de mine, dar m\'e3 voi mul\'fe
umi cu ceea ce-mi va oferi p\'e2n\'e3 la desp\'e3r\'feire. Mi-a ofer}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 it deja destule. Am primit mai mult}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 dec\'e2
t am visat toat\'e3 via\'fea. Chiar dac\'e3 din clipa asta n-a\'ba mai vedea-o, tot m\'e3 consider c\'e2\'batig\'e3tor.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu te cred, spuse Trevize cu bl\'e2nde\'fee. Socot c\'e3 }{\i\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 e\'bati}{\b\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{
\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 un prost\'e3nac romantic \'bai, pe cuv\'e2ntul meu, nici nu te-a\'ba vrea altfel. Janov, de\'bai nu ne cunoa\'batem de mult\'e3 vreme, am trecut \'eempreun\'e3 prin at\'e2tea \'een ultimele s\'e3pt\'e3m\'e2
ni... Iart\'e3-m\'e3 dac\'e3-\'fei par ridicol, dar \'fein foarte mult la tine.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai eu te pre\'feuiesc, Golan, \'eel asigur\'e3 Pelorat.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 N-a\'ba vrea s\'e3 suferi. Ar trebui s\'e3 m\'e3 la\'bai s\'e3 vorbesc cu Bliss.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu, nu. Te rog s\'e3 n-o faci. O s\'e3-i \'feii o predic\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af N-o s}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'e3-i \'fein nici o predic\'e3. Vreau s\'e3 vorbesc cu ea \'eentre patru ochi, dar nu neap\'e3rat \'een leg\'e3tur\'e3 cu tine. Te rog, Janov,}{
\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\sub\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 n-am inten\'feia de a face asta f\'e3r\'e3 asentimentul t\'e3u, a\'baa c\'e3 las\'e3-m\'e3 s\'e3 am o discu\'feie cu ea pentru a clarifica o serie de lucruri. Dac
\'e3 o s\'e3 fiu mul\'feumit, a s\'e3-\'fei adresez cele mai sincere felicit\'e3ri \'bai o s\'e3 r\'e3m\'e2n \'bai eu cu cugetul \'eemp\'e3cat, orice s-ar \'eent\'e2mpla dup\'e3 aceea.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 O s\'e3 strici totul, spuse Pelorat cl\'e3tin\'e2nd ne\'eencrez\'e3tor din cap.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'ce\'fei promit c\'e3 nu. Te }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 implor}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 .}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Bine, dar s\'e3 fii atent, drag\'e3 prietene...}{\f27\fs20 
