\par }{\i\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Mi-a zis Pel c\'e3 voiai s\'e3-mi vorbe\'bati.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Da, r\'e3spunse Trevize.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Bliss se afla \'een micul apartament ce-i fusese rezervat}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 lui Trevize.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Se a\'baez\'e3 cu elegan\'fe\'e3, \'bai puse picior peste picior. Ochii ei frumo\'bai \'bai limpezi \'eel privir\'e3 cercet\'e3tori. P\'e3rul lung \'bai negru avea reflexe aib\'e3strui.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu-\'fei prea sunt pe plac, a\'baa-i? M-ai privit dezaprobator \'eenc\'e3 de la \'eenceput.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 R\'e3mas \'een picioare, T}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 revize \'eei spuse:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20 \'ce}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'fei dai seama ce-i \'een mintea altora. \'aatii ce cred despre tine \'bai cuno\'bati motivul.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cu o u\'baoar\'e3 mi\'bacare din cap Bliss neg\'e3:
\par }{\i\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Mintea ta nu e \'eenc\'e3tu\'baat\'e3 de Gaia. \'aatii asta \'bai singur. Am avut nevoie de alegerea ta, c\'e3ci trebuia f\'e3cut\'e3 de o minte limpede \'ba
i neinfluen\'feat\'e3 din afara. C\'e2nd v-am capturat nava, tu \'bai Pelorat v-a\'fei aflat sub \'eenr\'e2urirea unui c\'e2mp calmant, dar acest lucru era esen\'feial. Din cauza panicii sau fricii se putea \'eent\'e2mpla ceva grav cu mintea ta, c\'e3
ci ar fi putut s\'e3-\'bai piard\'e3 calit\'e3\'feile \'bai s\'e3 nu ne foloseasc\'e3 la nimic \'een momentele cruciale care au urmat. At\'e2t \'bai nimic mai mult. N-am trecut dincolo de acest prag \'bai nici n-am f\'e3cut-o de atunci \'eencoace, a\'ba
a c\'e3 nu \'batiu la ce te referi.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Am f\'e3cut alegerea de care avea\'fei nevoie. Am hot\'e3r\'e2t \'een favoarea Gaiei \'bai a Galaxiei. Atunci de ce mai vorbim despre faptul c\'e3 mintea mea a}{
\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 r\'e3mas limpede \'bai neinfluen\'feat\'e3? A\'fei ob\'feinut ceea ce dorea\'fei \'bai acum pute\'fei face ce vre\'fei din mine.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Te \'een\'baeli profund, Trev. S-ar putea ca \'een viitor s\'e3 mai fie nevoie de luat hot\'e3r\'e2ri importante. Tu r\'e3m\'e2i ceea ce e\'bati \'bai, c\'e2t vei tr\'e3
i, te vom considera o resurs\'e3 natural\'e3 rar\'e3 a Galaxiei. F\'e3r\'e3 \'eendoial\'e3 c\'e3 s-ar putea s\'e3 existe sau s\'e3 mai apar\'e3 \'bai al\'feii ca tine \'een Galaxie, dar deocamdat\'e3 nu cunoa\'batem altul. \'cenc\'e3 nu-\'fe
i putem aduce nici o atingere.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize r\'e3mase pe g\'e2nduri.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Tu e\'bati Gaia, dar eu nu doresc s\'e3 vorbesc cu ea. Eu vreau}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 s\'e3-\'fei voebesc \'fe
ie, ca individ, dac\'e3 a\'baa ceva e posibil.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Se poate. Suntem departe de a duce o existen\'fe\'e3 comun\'e3. Pot bloca existen\'fea Gai}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 ei pentru un timp.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Da, spuse Trevize, cred c\'e3 po\'fei. Ai f\'e3cut-o \'een clipa asta?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Da.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Atunci d\'e3-mi voie s\'e3-\'fei spun c\'e3 n-ai jucat cinstit. Probabil c\'e3 n-ai p\'e3truns \'een mintea mea pentru a-mi influen\'fea hot\'e3r\'e2rea, dar sigur ai \'eenfluen\'fe
at-o pe a lui Pelorat, a\'baa-i?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 A\'baa \'fei s-a p\'e3rut?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Exact. \'cen momentul crucial, Pelorat mi-a amintit de viziunea pe care o avea el despre o Galaxie vie \'bai g\'e2ndul lui m-a determinat s\'e3 fac alegerea din acea clip\'e3. S-ar putea ca g
\'e2ndul s\'e3 fi fost al lui, dar mintea care-l inspirase era a ta, nu-i a\'baa?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 G\'e2ndul acesta, ca \'bai altele, existau \'een mintea lui. Am netezit calea \'bai activat ideea de Galaxie vie, dar nu \'een dauna altui g\'e2nd. Prin urmare, el a lunecat cu u\'baurin\'fe
\'e3 din con\'batiin\'fe\'e3 ajung\'e2nd s\'e3 fie exprimat \'een cuvinte. Te rog s\'e3 m\'e3}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  crezi, nu eu l-am creat. El se afla acolo.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Acest lucru poate fi totu\'bai considerat un amestec direct \'een libertatea total\'e3 pe care o aveam pentru a lua o hot\'e3r\'e2re, nu? }{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Gaia a socotit c\'e3 e necesar.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 A socotit? Atunci, \'een speran\'fea c\'e3 asta te-ar putea face s\'e3 te sim\'fei mai bine sau mai nobil\'e3, vreau s\'e3 \'batii c\'e3 de\'bai remarca lui Janov m-a convins s\'e3 iau hot\'e3r
\'e2rea \'een acel moment, eu a\'ba fi f\'e3cut aceea\'bai alegere chiar dac\'e3 n-ar fi scos o vorb\'e3 sau dac\'e3 ar fi \'eencetat s\'e3 m\'e3 determine s\'e3 aleg \'een alt fel. \'dein foarte mult s\'e3 cuno\'bati acest fapt.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 M\'e3 simt u\'baurat\'e3, \'eei r\'e3spunse Bliss cu r\'e3ceal\'e3. Asta e tot ce voiai s\'e3-mi comunici c\'e2nd \'fei-ai exprimat dorin\'fea de a m\'e3 vedea?
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Nu.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Mai e ceva?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize se a\'baez\'e3 pe un scaun pe care-l pusese \'een fa\'fea ei, astfel c\'e3 genunchiili se atinser\'e3. Se aplec\'e3 spre ea \'bai spuse:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 C\'e2nd ne-am apropiat de Gaia, tu erai de serviciu pe sta\'feia spa\'feial\'e3. Tu ne-ai capturat; tu ai venit s\'e3 ne iei \'bai de atunci ai r\'e3mas tot timpul cu noi, cu excep\'fe
ia mesei pe care am luat-o cu Dom, c\'e2nd n-ai fost de fa\'fe\'e3. \'aai \'eenc\'e3 ceva. Tot tu te-ai aflat pe }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Far Star }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 cu noi c\'e2nd am luat hot\'e3r\'e2
rea. Mereu tu.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Eu sunt Gaia.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Explica\'feia nu m\'e3 satisface. Un iepure \'eenseamn\'e3 Gaia. Chiar \'bai o pietricic\'e3 \'eenseamn\'e3 Gaia, dar nu toate reprezint\'e3 Gaia \'een aceea\'bai m\'e3sur\'e3. Unele s}{
\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 unt mai importante. Dar de ce tocmai tu?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Tu ce crezi?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Trevize las\'e3 deoparte orice re\'feinere:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Eu cred c\'e3 tu nu e\'bati Gaia. Reprezin\'fei mai mult de-at\'e2t.
\par Bliss \'ee\'bai \'feuguie buzele \'bai scoase un sunet dispre\'feuitor. Trevize nu se d\'e3du b\'e3tut:}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20 \'ce}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 n momentele c\'e2nd }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 trebuia s\'e3 iau hot\'e3r\'e2rea, femeia care se afla \'eempreun\'e3 cu Oratorul...}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 El \'eei spunea Novi.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 A\'baa, aceast\'e3 Novi a afirmat c\'e3 robo\'feii, care acum nu mai}{\b\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 exist\'e3, au \'ee
ndrumat Gaia pe drumul acesta \'bai au educat-o s\'e3 urmeze o versiune a celor trei Legi ale Roboti}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 cii.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Foarte adev\'e3rat.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai robo\'feii nu mai exist\'e3?
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af A}{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'baa a spus Novi.}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Novi }{\i\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 nu }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 a spus a\'baa ceva. \'cemi amintesc exact cuvintele ei: "Gaia s-a format cu mii de ani \'een urm
\'e3 cu ajutorul robo\'feilor care, pentru o scurt\'e3 perioad\'e3, au slujit speciei umane, dar acu}{\f27\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 m n-o mai fac."
\par }{\f446\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Trev, }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'bai asta \'eenseamn\'e3 c\'e3 ei mai exist\'e3?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu, \'eenseamn\'e3 c\'e3 nu mai slujesc omenirii. Dar n-ar putea c\'e2rmui?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ridicol\'e3 idee!}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Sau supraveghea? De ce te aflai acolo \'een momentul hot\'e3r\'e2rii? Nu p\'e3reai at\'e2t de important\'e3. Novi a condus tratativele \'bai ea reprezenta Gaia. Ce nevoie era de tine? Doar dac
\'e3 nu cumva...}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ei bine? Doar dac\'e3 ce?}{\f27\fs20 
\par }{\f446\fs20 \'af }{\f443\fs20\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Doar dac\'e3 nu cumva tu e\'bati supraveghetorul care are rolul de a aprecia dac\'e3 Gaia respect\'e3 sau nu cele Trei Legi. Doar dac\'e3 tu nu e\'bati cumva un robot at\'e2t de
 iscusit construit \'eenc\'e2t nimeni nu te poate deosebi de o fiin\'fe\'e3 uman\'e3.}{\f27\fs20 
